data.oai_dc:dc: Reads from HEK293-PGBD5-PBwt mapped to hg19+pb-ef1-neo

Reads obtained from sequencing FLEA PCR products to amplify transposon reporter insertions in sample HEK293-PGBD5-PBwt, filtered, quality trimmed and mapped to a hybrid genome consisting of hg19 and the reporter plasmid sequence. Reads were mapped with bwa-mem using default parameters.
